CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Great Southern Bancorp Inc is a bank holding company. It is principally engaged in the business of originating residential and commercial real estate loans, construction loans, commercial business loans, and consumer loans. The bank provides various services such as Business Banking, Merchant Services, Debit and Credit cards, Online Banking, Mobile Banking, VIP Banking, Overdraft Protection, and other related services.
